More deeply than their backs.
Yes, these men and women were the stars of the show for me.
They had waited for this moment all their lives, as their predecessors of the Middle Ages had eagerly awaited the end of the world, and as my grandmother was waiting for the Oprah Winfrey Show on Channel 8, every day, at 4pm.
And as she went to the altar, I was hiding behind her, for I was absolutely certain that my grandmother would go to Heaven.
